posting_body: ['Arbors at Edgewood', '10304 20th St E, Edgewood, WA, 98372', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 106', 'OR Text', '106', 'to', 'show contact info', 'for more information.', 'Interested in more information?', 'See link below:', '<URL>', 'THE ARBORS AT EDGEWOOD', 'This is a 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1121 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Welcome to the newest apartment community in the Pacific Northwest.', 'Immersed in rich cultural history, the community of Edgewood, WA offers the perfect combination of work-life balance.', 'The Arbors at Edgewood apartments includes a wide range of modern amenities catered to make your life easier.', 'Being close to the outdoors while also minutes from I-5 and downtown Tacoma is a commuter’s dream and an offering that we are proud to provide.', 'At The Arbors at Edgewood, you can choose a layout that perfectly fits your needs.', 'Escape to your own oasis within one of our spacious one, two, and three bedroom apartments.', 'We spare no expense to ensure that your home at our pet-friendly community provides everything you need and more.', 'Pet Policy', 'Maximum 2 total pets per household', '$25 monthly rent per pet', 'Deposit: $200 cats / $300 dogs', 'One-time Fee: $200 per cat / $300 per dog', 'Breed restrictions apply', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Saturday-Sunday:10:00AM-5:00PM', 'DLmj9OzAvfon']
